data.description: Beautiful new construction in the highly desired neighborhood of Tiburon. Lovely interiors in soft neutral colors, wood flooring, designer granite through out, exposed & painted brick walls & cypress beam between family room & kitchen. Formal dining room & eat-in kitchen. Spacious remote master suite with spa-like bath. Great out door living space includes covered patio area, out door kitchen and large back yard. Unfinished bonus room is ready and set up with electricity and plumbing.
